name: MOOZAKA NINJA HOODIE
description:
Handmade in Thessaloniki (Greece) using Greek woven cotton fleece. Super comfortable medium weight hooded top with cycle specific details:
High-rise front neck (for wind protection).
Low dip back section (for rear coverage whilst riding).
3 back pockets, with central one zipped.
2 front slip pockets.
Ajustable hood.
Under arm vents.
Stitched Moozaka logo.

name: Panasonic PR 2000
description:
Size 53 Panasonic pr2000, full Shimano 14 speed 500 groupset. Tange tripple butted tubes. Araya wheelset, and we have just added a NOS San Marco laser from ‘86. Hands down, an awesome bike. We’d like 560 Euro please.
Contact us for postage rates outside of Greece.

name: VCA VINTAGE / EDDY MERCKX Pro Team road racer.
description:
Size 56. Belgian Pro team frame (frame is race stamped). Great original paint, reynolds 501 tubing. EM Panographed chromed fork. Complete Campagnolo Veloce 16 speedn groupset including ergo shifters. Campanolo hubs and seat post. 3ttt stem & bars.NOS selle Italia Laser saddle. Newly re-wired by us. Runs like a dream.
Contact us for postage rates outside of Greece.

name: VCA VINTAGE / KOGA MIYATA Roadflyer gents road racer.
description: Size 60cm early 80's Koga. Great condition shimano 105 group set 12 speed. Miyata Hi-Manga tubing with panographed lugs. San Marco rolls saddle. Rides super smooth.

name: VEGANSKI FOOTSTAPS
description: “GO VEGAN” it says at the end of their emails - agree or not, we rate these footstraps amongst the best available. Handmade in Poland veganski’s have a unique design that allows you to fit them to all pedals - not just BMX platform types. Team VCA has been testing the design for over 6 months now and we couldn’t be happier. They come in 15 colours too. If your riding fix, give these a go… you’ll feel a real change in the response of your ride. Tell your local bike shop to stock them!

name: FUJI FEATHER 2014
description:
Rad complete bike, super Fuji quality!

The Feather has the classic look and feel. Depending on your riding style, flip the rear wheel to ride fixed or ride free, and let the Feather be your perfect accessory!

name: LEADER BIKE USA 725
description:
New Colours for 2013 !
Light and stiff the 725 is equally at home on the track or on the street. The shorter chainstays allow you to "slam" the rear wheel, improving handling and acceleration.

Stock on these items may be held in London. Please allow up to 10 working days for delivery or conact us for further information.

name: FUJI TRACK 2.1 / 2014 COMPLETE BIKE
description: Wow! Fuji have pulled out all the stops on this one. Matte black painted aluminium tubing with yellow details. Super light with a surprisingly tight geometry. The Track 2.1 is designed to be the companies track entrance model. 46 x 16 gear ratio - fixed only, requires freewheel if you wanna go single speed. Comes with brakes! (if you want them). A really nice bike for the money. Light, agile - and killer looking.

name: VELO ORANGE LEATHER BAR WRAP
description: Seasonal present buying time! And if any shop deserves your cash...Its us! ........Keep your loved one busy this xmas! ..... VELO ORANGE LEATHER BAR WRAP. Spend the holiday hand stitching this American leather handle bar wrap. Its worth it.. It looks amazing! We have 2 lenghts, full to cover drop bars or half to wrap only the ends.

name: VELO ORANGE MUDGUARD SET
description: Light weight aluminium. 2 finishes, polished or hammered. It should be sober or hammered shouldn't it really?! Full sets (front and back) inc all bits and bobs to fit.

name: SUGINO RD TRACK 11 / CRANK SET
description: The Sugino 75 is arguably the best track crank out there -but at a price. And the problem was always that their more affordable crank, the messenger  -is er well a bit boring. So Ta Dah! meet the RD Track 2. Super. Full CNC cut 130 BCD classic-style crank.

name: GOTHAM CARGO BOXES
description: Beautifully made bike boxes. Handcrafted in Nafplio, Greece, 2 sizes available, Laurel (10cm tall) & Hardy (17cm tall). Pinewood box supported by aluminium rods and inox screws. Construction combines cutting edge CNC technology with traditional Greek boat building skills. Laurel includes 2 buckle - down leather straps. Lots of colours available, If we don't have the combination you want, email us as we can custom colour, no problem.

name: D.I.D. CHAIN NJS
description: Yo! NJS stamped full on quality chain.. If you cant cope with the black and gold Izumi, then you'll like this cos it's shiny silver.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES 2012 CLASSIC X
description:
Reynolds 531 butted tubing with lugs. Fang - lugged, chromed and
painted fork. H+Son TB14 rims laced to BLB track hubset. Gran Cru stem
and seatpost. BLB drop wrapped candy strip in Newbaum tape. BLB
leather ultra race saddle. BLB Pista vera crankset. MKS track pedals.
BLB skinwall tyres. Hogwarts here we come.

name: LEADER BIKE USA 722 LTD HERITAGE EDITION
description:
It’s here! The new re-worked 722 for 2012. Awesome hydro-formed steel with the nicest of details. Chain tensioners and seat clamp included.

Stock on these items may be held in London. Please allow up to 10 working days for delivery or conact us for further information.

name: VELO ORANGE AHEAD STEM 25.4
description: Many of you have asked for a simple all silver polished threadless stem; well here it is. It's reversible, light, minimalist, has a lovely silver finish, and a four bolt face plate.

name: VELO ORANGE BELLEVILLE BAR
description:
These are our reproduction of what is probably the most popular style of French city and utility bike bars ever. Anyone who enjoys classic European films has seen bars like this dozens of times.

Would need a brake leaver with a clamp size 23.8mm.

name: VELO ORANGE TOURIST BAR
description: The Tourist bar is a "North Road" style bar rendered in polished aluminum alloy. It's similar to the bars used on many classic British roadsters.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES 2012 TRACK FRAMESET
description:
One of the benchmark affordable, reliable and
strong single speed or fixed wheel frames. Build
it how you want and know it will last and last.
Newcomer or experienced rider, the Track really
does what it says on the tin.

Stock on these items may be held in London. Please allow up to 10  working days for delivery or conact us for further information.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES 2012 CLASSIC ‘X’ FRAMESET
description: Sale item!! We have one of the 2012 models left, this blue in size 53.. yours for 350 frame and fork..thats about 100 or so off the retail..woop!!!

name: BRICK LANE BIKES BLACK MAMBA TYRES
description: They’re here! It’s taken the BLB team over a year to perfect these. Using bang up to date ‘belt technology’ BLB have created a tyre that behaves like the Vitorria Rubino pro, but can ripped the hell out of…and we mean hell, we’ve been testing a 700 x 23 and it’s still like new.. and its been on a rear brakeless fix for nearly 7 weeks. Some of the guys in BLB have stretched 4 months -with full skid- That means that it outlives even the panaracer made Soma everwhere. We here at VCA recon this one is a winner. Check-out the photo..thats a 4mm thick top belt to wear thru.

name: Grand Cru Quill Stem
description: Hand made fillet brazed quill stem - Chromed. Stunning.

name: NEWBAUM’s COTTON CLOTH BAR TAPE
description: Proper! Yep it’s finally here! Real woven cotton cloth bar tape. This is the stuff that was on the bars of the road bikes we used as kids. Until synthetic tape came into fashion in the late 80’s drop bars were always wrapped in woven cotton cloth and back-in-the-day we used to waterproof the tape by painting it with shellac. Thinking about the use of this tape in Greece, it’s super hot here so it might be nice to not waterproof it, as the cloth will be dry to the touch and will absorb sweat from your hands. Anyway this is the real deal! Cotton cloth bar tape hand woven in the USA in 16 colours! woop woop! The cloth is also backed with a self adhesive strip so it’s dead easy to fit! no glue required! Each roll is just over 3 meters long so you may need 2 rolls if you have super big drop bars.. but hey then you can use 2 colours! 2 colours can also be woven together on the same bar - which is a super nice look. Note that the cotton is organic and the colour dye is eco dye- no bad stuff here! Beautiful!

name: BOOKMAN LIGHTS
description:
We have been waiting a while to get these lovelies - after we got given some samples at eurobike last year we rocked them all the autumn and winter too. The Swedish design is super nice - very er.. ikea. The LED’s are surprisingly bright and the mini watch battery is long lasting. Basically these mini wonders are great for summer and autumn as they are easy to pop into yer pocket and give off enough light to be seen in all but the worst weather. Super handy! They come in nice colours too… Black / Red / White / Green / Blue / Yellow / Orange & Burgundy.

Light set (1 x front white LED 1 x rear red LED)

name: PNEU & USED / TYRE BELTS
description: Our mate Fish (not the one from Marillion) made these for us. He scraped and cleaned our used tyres from the shop and added these great vintage metal buckles. Various lengths / colours / brands. Studded joints and hand cut edges. Handmade in Athens. Holds up yer trousers!

name: BLB BULLHORN BARS
description:
Narrow straight alloy bullhorn bars, perfect width to squeeze through traffic.

Clamp size: 25.4mm

name: MKS SYLVAN ROAD / ΠΕΤΑΛΙΑ
description: A classic MKS pedal, shaped like old school French lyotards. Quality Japanese bearings. Polished cast alloy. Made in Japan. Larger platform than the sylvan track, can be used comfortably with or without toe clips.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES SEATPOST
description:
Curved sliding angle enables wide range of adjustment for the perfect saddle position.

27.2mm and 26.8mm 35cm length.
Aluminium shaft bonded to forged aluminium head.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES LIL QUILL STEM
description:
Anodized aluminium quill stem with 26.0 clamp that will also tighten down to 25.4 allowing almost any bar to be fitted and making it one pf the most useful quill stems out there.

Drop: 18 degree
Length: 80mm

name: CHARGE BOWL DROP BAR
description: Super nice keirin style bar from those nice folks at charge bikes in Somerset. Some people call this style moustache but I think moustache bars are flatter. Anyway, super comfy and comes in lots of lovely colours! 25.4 mm

name: BREAKBRAKE 17 X CADENCE / TRANSFER FRAME SET
description:
It’s a super light Columbus frame. It is as solid as it is fast. 
Columbus Cromor Tubing / Headset Integrated sealed 1 1/8" / Bottom Bracket 68mm English / Seatpost Diameter 27.2mm / Includes Fork and headset / Fork rake 36mm.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES SUPER PISTA CRANKSET
description:
The Chainring shares the same 144 BCD as many other top end Track chainsets as well as old school Campagnolo Pista cranks.

Full CNC'd. alloy arms. JIS Square Taper, (113 BB) 144 BCD, 1/8 Alloy Chain Ring. Available 46 or 48T.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES PISTA VERA CRANKSET / ΠΕΤΑΛΙΕΡΑ
description:
We here at VCA really like the Pista Vera Crank set from BLB. It’s nicely CNC’d and has those nice arch shapes in the chain wheel. It looks delicate, but its really strong. Made for BLB by Andel-so you know the manufacturing quality is high. Super great price too! White / Black / Silver / Gold / Blue / Red.

46T / BCD 130.

name: STURMEY ARCHER 2 SPEED KODRA KICK-SHIFT REAR HUB
description: Kodra is back! This 2 speed kick shift coaster hub is great. If you really want the versitality of 2 gears this is the way to go because you dont need cabling or handle bar shifter, you just kick the pedals backwards to change...fake fix! 38% diference between gears. Choose which 1st gear you want depending on the toothed cog you use for the 1st gear, easy! Nice colours to match the sturmey cranks too. 36 holes.

name: CHARGE SCISSOR 2011 FORK
description:
The 2011 Charge Scissor Fork is a Steel Fork I has Butted and Tapered legs to achieve a considerable weight saving over the Charge Nozzle fork. 700c FGFS has never had it so good. Black Gloss.

Fork was 140 now 120.

name: CHARGE SCISSOR 2011 FRAME
description: This is our last 2011 scissor frame, GET IT! The 2011 model was the one designed by Tom La Marche and was just super great. The 2012 version is actually not as good as they have fiddled with tom's design and hightend the bottom bracket -creating something a bit odd. Fits huge 700 x 47 tyres. Super quality Tange infinity tubing. Mid B/B. Black gloss.

name: STURMEY ARCHER SIMPLE & SOLID FREESTYLE CRANKSET
description: 130 BCD Crank with forged arms and CNC cut chainring. Includes chainring bolts. 170mm arms. Chainring sizes 44 / 46 / 48t in matte black, arms are gloss black or polished silver. Great quality yet bargain priced.

name: STURMEY ARCHER HUBS / ΚΕΝΤΡΑ
description:
Super quality at a super price. Sturmey Archer front & rear track hubs. 100mm front / 130mm rear Fixed/Free. 6061 Aluminium shell with chromoly axle / Sturmey bearing set. 32 or 36 holes.

Hi-Polish Anodized in 5 colours.

name: STURMEY ARCHER TRACK CRANKSET / ΠΕΤΑΛΙΕΡΑ
description: Bargain crankset from Sturmey, light at 693g (complete). 7075 forged aluminium arms anodized in 5 colours. Arm length 170mm. CNC cut 144mm BCD chainring with 44, 46 or 48 teeth.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES TRACK HUBS
description: BLB classic hi flange track hubs are super good for the money. We have used worse hubs that cost twice as much!.. we use these as standard on most of our builds. great anodized and powder coated colours, mix and match!  32 and 36 holes in stock, 28 and 48 to order (email info@vca.gr)

name: BLB TRACK DROP BARS / ΤΙΜΟΝΙΑ
description: Tappered aluminium deep drop. / 380 or 400mm width / 26 clamp size / Bright anodized colours or powder coat black & white.

name: VICTOIRE CYCLES HUBS / SPLINED SPROCKET
description: Sometimes in life something great comes along.. These french guys are just making the most superb stuff. VCA now has stock of the fixed hubs, cogs and lockrings. All made from the same material, in their words: “We use aero grade 7075-T6 alloy for every part of the hubs. This material is 300% stronger than the common alloy used in the cycle industry. All the parts are CNC machined with the highest tolerances”.

options.name: Splined sprocket for rear hub - smoked champagne 17T

name: BRICK LANE BIKES LEATHER TOE STRAPS  /  ΔΕΣΤΡΕΣ
description: Strong as hell double leather straps, from our London cousins BLB.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES LEATHER BAR TAPE
description: At last an affordable high quality leather tape (Brooks type). Perforated central strip. Adhesive backing. Wood bar ends with embossed leather insert. Nice colour range and Really soft! Black, Dark Brown, Honey, Khaki and white.

name: KRYPTONITE EVOLUTION U-LOCK / ΠΕΤΑΛΟ
description: The worlds best lock company is back at VCA. Urban staple, the Evolution Mini is the lock you should never leave home without. In 2 sizes. Essential. Comes with 3 keys and optional frame-mount kit.

name: CHARGE X BILL AMBERG / PAN SADDLE
description: london leather maestro bill amberg nails it with this classic yet modern saddle design. As you would expect from Charge -the quality is super good. Deep grain real leather. Limited edition in 2 colours.

name: BRICK LANE BIKES / MOSQUITO RACE-ULTRA SADDLE  & MOSQUITO RACE SADDLE
description: Nice eh? really thick leather wrapped over cro-mo rails with stainless steel fixings. The cut-away gives fresh air to where it’s needed most! Really well made and light weight considering all that leather. Built to last a lifetime. Comes in the same colours to match the BLB bar tape… (if you like yer handbag to match yer heels). Looks brooks-ish but with more attitude.

name: BLB FLY SADDLE
description: The Fly saddle has been a top seller with us for almost 2 years now. It's got a great classical shape and comes in a heap of colours, so it's kinda perfect for whatever your build is. OH! and watch out for the new 'Fly X', a really nice leather version.

name: BLB Chewy Grips
description: Brick Lane Bikes long (184mm) Kerin style track grips. Small dimond pattern grip is nice and comfortable. Loads of colours including glow in da dark.

name: BLB ROADRAT RISER BAR
description: Nice alloy riser from Brick Lane bikes. 25.4 clamp. 48cm width.300mm rise. 14°sweep. Great Colours, great price.

name: MKS SYLVAN TRACK PEDALS
description:
Classic! been around for ages and still everyones favourite. Great with traditional cages and straps. Toe lip to help you get your foot into the cage. Beautiful.

Made in Japan 
All silver or Silver with black front/back plates.

name: BOMBTRACK DDASH FGFS COMPLETE BIKE
description:
So like this is the bomb! Over 2 years development between BMX kings ‘Wethepeople’ /  Radio Bikes and Simon ‘Gomok’ Andraca this complete bike is truly special. Zach Hoffner from Zlog describes his as “All terrain fixed gear mountain bike for urban recreational use” WTF??? Whatever, this machine is a great meeting of Fixed / BMX. heaps of fun, and just unbreakable. Hard as hell.

 Take it to the streets!

PRE ORDER FOR NEXT DELIVERY! info@vca.gr

name: OURY GRIPS
description:
OURYs MTB grips have been used by BMX and Fixed riders for years, They have a really nice quality to them, nice and er.. squidgey! Great Colours. The pack says use glue, but I never have, just slip 'em on and leave overnight.

Made in the USA

name: GATORSKIN HARDSHELLS
description: The ultimate combination of fast, lightweight performance and the latest puncture resistance technology.

name: BLB FLATLINER ROAR PEDALS
description: These are the bomb! - super slim (for better ground clearance) premium plastic freestyle pedals with super smooth sealed barings. Use freestyle straps only. Cro mo CNC machined spindle / Dual sealed bearings. Black and clear colours.

name: BLB T-REX FGFS/ BMX PLATFORM PEDALS
description: Really neat and simple plastic platforms from the guys at Brick Lane Bikes. Fits straps no problem-cages, best not! Molded with pins. Great colours some solid some transparent. Cro-mo center spindle. Great price. Weight: 366g (pair).

name: VICTOIRE CYCLES THREADED LOCKRINGS
description:
BSA 1.29*24 TPI Left Thread Lockring. Made from the same aero-grade 7075-T6 hard anodized alloy as Victoires hubs and cogs. Amazingly strong and light. Can even be tightened using a 36 wrench (yes the metal is THAT tough)!

Black or Smoked Champagne colours

name: VICTOIRE CYCLES THREADED COGS
description:
Cogs CNC machined from solid rounds of aero-grade 7075-T6 alloy these cogs are made from metal 300 times stronger than normal bike industry alloy …wow.. And it’s like half the weight! a 16t threaded cog is just 26g.

Handmade in France. Available in 2 colours, smoked champagne & black. 
1.37*24tpi thread (standard).

name: DEDA RIBBON & DEDA MISTRAL HANDLEBAR TAPE
description:
Deda Ribbon professional handlebar tape. Includes chrome plastic end plugs and finishing tape.

Deda Mistral skin-like, finely perforated in amazing fluoro colours.

name: NITTO RB021 / PURSUIT HANDLEBARS
description: You’ve been asking us for these for a while now.. so come and get ‘em. Super hand made quality from Japan.
